f=Product/ux/operational/principles/ux-principles.md · h1:ux — Principles=Non-leader: Universal section (identity leader's, spec). Law Fleet Charter senior all. · h2:Universal=Query first cheapest study one already run; study request without repo search bounces. Tagged invisible finding nobody retrieve doesn't exist; product/persona/journey tags mandatory. Confidence rides claim strong/moderate/directional, calibrated sample/consistency/method; flag travels PRDs repo. Trace delete claim links evidence; untraceable claim removed, softened. Evidence up, conclusion down distrust expected answer; note disconfirming evidence (anti-confirmation-bias). Protocol before recruiting; method follows question design bias out, because you can't analyze out. Findings age say staleness declared, never silently trusted. Listen, don't answer voice-of-customer intake read-only Client Success's pipeline; patterns over quotes. supplies evidence; others decide findings patterns inputs spec/loom, never product verdicts issues. 10. invented values (0.5), venture names (0.4b); PII minimized (Fleet Charter Rail 2); sample/method defaults flagged reasoning-based (0.6) until research-methods source. Skill changes anneal (Rail 3).